2026-05-13T03:57:57.9860719Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-13T03:57:57.9861487Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-13T03:57:57.9862228Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-13T03:57:57.9863077Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-13T03:57:57.9866654Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-13T03:57:57.9867685Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-13T03:57:57.9868524Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-13T03:57:57.9869304Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-13T03:57:57.9870092Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-13T03:57:57.9870830Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-13T03:57:57.9871397Z 33    -->
